On Tuesday may 9th my debut picture book was finally published! ❤️ 

I had the most amazing launching I could ever imagine at @borisandhorton surrounded by my family, friends and the amazing community of dog lovers and art lovers that I’ve met through my years in nyc.

It was really a dream come true. My Dog Just Speaks Spanish is a story about best friends, language, immigration and love ❤️ 

Thank you for everybody that came❤️ I couldn’t be more grateful.

And for those who couldn’t you can find my book on Amazon, Barnes and noble, target and many other stores ❤️ if you buy before Sunday I’m offering free pet portraits ❤️ just send me a pic of the book or purchase confirmation. (Ps. My store is close until holidays so this might be one of the only ways to get a portrait) 

I love you all bye ❤️

Happy Mother’s Day to all moms who love big and wide! 

I have been so lucky in my life! My mom is one of the most wonderful and stronger persons I know! She taught me about unconditional love, and I am who I am because of her. Mother’s Day is always hard because we are far away, I embrace her life lessons and always dream of the next time I will see her ❤️ 

But I AM so lucky, I have another mom now. Someone who without knowing me accept me in her house and family and made me feel at home even when we couldn’t really understand each other at first

To both of them, and all the other amazing moms in my life happy Mother’s Day! 🥹❤️ for more big and wide love .
